headline: S&P Global Introduces S&P Global Energy
summary: S&P Global (NYSE: SPGI) announced S&P Global Energy as the new name and identity for its Commodity Insights division at the company's 2025 Investor Day. S&P Global Energy reflects the division's strategic focus on providing world-leading benchmarks, data, and insights that enable its customers to plan, act, and thrive in a rapidly expanding and evolving global energy ecosystem.
